<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Legend Details - Queen Marika</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark sticky-top">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand font-weight-bold" href="/mvc/characters">ELDEN RING GALLERY</a>
        <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/mvc/characters">Home</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/mvc/characters/about">About</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/mvc/characters/new">Add Character</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

    <main class="container mb-5">
        <div class="detail-container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                    <img src="images/marika_full.jpg" alt="Queen Marika the Eternal" class="hero-img">
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h1 class="display-3 text-warning">Queen Marika</h1>
                    <h4 class="accent-text mb-4">The Eternal • Vessel of the Elden Ring</h4>
                    
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h3>Backstory</h3>
                        <p class="fs-5">
                            Queen Marika the Eternal is the sovereign of the Lands Between and the mother of the demigods. As an Empyrean, she was chosen by the Greater Will to become the vessel for the Elden Ring, establishing the Golden Order that ruled the world for ages.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h3>Abilities & Role</h3>
                        <p class="accent-text">
                            "The Queen's sorrow was great, but her ambition was greater."
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Divine Power:</strong> Capability to shatter or reform the Elden Ring.</li>
                            <li><strong>Golden Grace:</strong> Bestows or removes the "Grace" from the inhabitants of the Lands Between.</li>
                            <li><strong>Dual Nature:</strong> Exists in a mysterious, physical duality with Radagon of the Golden Order.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h3>Personality</h3>
                        <p>
                            Enigmatic and calculating, Marika's personality shifted from a faithful tool of the Greater Will to a rebellious figure who ultimately shattered the Ring, plunging the world into the Shattering.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-gold px-5">Back to Gallery</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="container text-center py-4">
        <p class="text-muted">Levi Duquette | UNCG CSC340</p>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>